data.meta_description: Looking for statistics on the fastest, tallest or longest roller coasters?  Find it all and much more with the interactive Roller Coaster Database.
data.text: Arrangement13 cars. Riders are arranged 4 across in a single row for a total of 4 riders per car.Primeval Whirl is really two distinct roller coaster placed side by side. Since they are completely independent of each other two entries exist in the database. This entry is for the northern of the two roller coasters.
